analysisPopulations.name: Full Analysis Set
analysisPopulations.text: All patients who have been randomized to study treatment will be included in the full analysis set (FAS) irrespective of their protocol adherence and continued participation in the study. Patients will be analysed according to their randomized IP assignment, irrespective of the treatment actually received.
analysisPopulations.label: FAS
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: All patients who have been randomized to study treatment will be included in the full analysis set (FAS) irrespective of their protocol adherence and continued participation in the study. Patients will be analysed according to their randomized IP assignment, irrespective of the treatment actually received.

analysisPopulations.name: Safety Analysis Set
analysisPopulations.text: All randomized patients who received at least one dose of study treatment. Patients will be analysed according to the treatment actually received.
analysisPopulations.label: SAF
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: All randomized patients who received at least one dose of study treatment. Patients will be analysed according to the treatment actually received.
analysisPopulations.criteria: Randomized AND received >=1 dose of study treatment

characteristics.name: Type 2 diabetes (T2D) status
characteristics.description: Established diagnosis of T2D or HbA1c more or equal to 6.5% (48 mmol/mol) shown at central laboratory test at enrolment
